_tags.description: This is the West Peak of Mt. Daniel. From several trip reports reported to be slightly higher than the East Peak which is marked as Mount Daniel on the map. West Peak is in King County by a small margin.
_tags.name: Mount Daniel
North Cadet Peak
_tags.note: USGS maps show this peak (7197') as being higher than Cadet Peak proper (7186'), but this is an error. North Cadet's true elevation is between 7160' and 7180'.
